casebody.data:
Jihye NAM, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Sungtae KIM, Defendant-Movant. M-1021 September Term 2018
081160 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs is granted, in part. The award of counsel fees is reduced to the amount of $5,552.50 and costs to the amount of $152.00, for a total award of $5,704.50.
